  <p style="font-size:14px;margin-bottom:0;"><strong>Type:</strong> Copper-binding tripeptide &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Molecular Weight:</strong> 403.9 g/mol &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Natural Source:</strong> Human plasma, saliva, urine &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Primary Actions:</strong> Collagen synthesis, wound healing, anti-inflammatory, antioxidant &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Topical Penetration:</strong> Excellent (small molecular weight) &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Optimal pH:</strong> 5.5&ndash;6.0</p>
